# poetry-pypirc

Sets poetry repository configs from a `.pypirc` file.

```bash
pip install poetry-pypirc
```

To use ~/.pypirc
```bash
poetry-pypirc
```

To use another pypirc file (`test.pypirc`)
```bash
poetry-pypirc test.pypirc
```
